&lt;h2&gt;&lt;iframe src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/GI_oKhoqZ80?feature=shared&quot; width=&quot;560&quot; height=&quot;314&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;br&gt;In a nutshell&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;767&quot; data-end=&quot;1177&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;Products are the heart of Picnic, and Fruits &amp;amp; Vegetables are the ultimate test of our promise to customers. In this role, you won’t just manage a category—you will own a dynamic, living ecosystem where freshness, seasonality, and razor-sharp pricing intersect.&amp;nbsp;At Picnic, we differentiate ourselves through data. We don&#39;t rely on gut feelings; we build our strategies on state-of-the-art data infrastructure. As Category Manager for Fruits &amp;amp; Vegetables, your superpower will be marrying elite analytical insights with deep market knowledge and a robust supplier network. Together with your cross-functional team, you’ll take end-to-end accountability for building an irresistible assortment, optimizing complex supply chains, minimizing waste, and driving massive commercial growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Tricks of the trade&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;11,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;11,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Data-Driven Category Ownership:&lt;/strong&gt; Dive into Picnic’s data warehouses to track performance, predict trends, and uncover commercial opportunities that optimize assortment, pricing, and promotion strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;11,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Commercial &amp;amp; Negotiation Mastery:&lt;/strong&gt; Lead end-to-end negotiations with growers, importers, and wholesalers. Secure competitive commercial terms and long-term volume commitments while building sustainable, trusting partnerships.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;11,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;11,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Fresh Logistics &amp;amp; Agility:&lt;/strong&gt; Own the unique challenges of the F&amp;amp;V supply chain. Proactively mitigate risks like sudden weather impacts, harvest fluctuations, and import restrictions to guarantee maximum product availability and shelf-life.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;11,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;11,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Wastage &amp;amp; Quality Control:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate closely with Quality Assurance and Supply Chain teams to optimize transit times, rethink packaging for sustainability and freshness, and keep food waste to an absolute minimum.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;11,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;11,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Innovation &amp;amp; Sourcing:&lt;/strong&gt; Spot upcoming food trends, drive local sourcing initiatives, and introduce eco-friendly innovations that excite our customers and elevate Picnic’s sustainability profile.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-path-to-node=&quot;11,5,0&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;11,5,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the strategic bridge between analysts, supply chain planners, and operations teams to execute flawless daily execution and long-term category goals.&lt;/li&gt;
